## 📊 FILE MAPPING - MANA KE MANA

```
BEFORE                          →    AFTER
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
auth.py (functions)             →    core/security.py
auth.py (env vars)              →    core/config.py
auth.py (imports ke routers)    →    routers/auth.py (unchanged)

database.py (URL)               →    core/config.py
database.py (SessionLocal)      →    database.py (unchanged)

main.py (calculate_haversine)   →    utils/helpers.py
main.py (menit_ke_jam)          →    utils/helpers.py
main.py (classify_store)        →    utils/helpers.py
main.py (calculate_routes logic) →   services/vrp_service.py
main.py (upload_sap_file)       →    services/order_service.py

geocoding.py (semua fungsi)     →    services/geocoding_service.py
vrp_solver.py (semua fungsi)    →    services/vrp_service.py

seed_data.py                    →    scripts/seed_data.py (pindah ke folder)
seed_armada.py                  →    scripts/seed_armada.py (pindah ke folder)
init_db.py                      →    scripts/init_db.py (pindah ke folder)
create_admin.py                 →    scripts/create_admin.py (pindah ke folder)

dependencies.py                 →    TETAP (tapi import dari core/security.py)
models.py                       →    TETAP di root (besar, no need move)
schemas.py                      →    TETAP di root (besar, no need move)
main.py                         →    TETAP di root tapi CLEANER (import dari modules)
```

---

## 🔄 DEPENDENCY FLOW (SETELAH REFACTOR)

```
REQUEST (HTTP) 
    ↓
routers/ (handlers)
    ↓
services/ (business logic)
    ↓
utils/ (helpers)
    ↓
models/ & database
    ↓
DATABASE

SECURITY:
requests → dependencies.py → core/security.py ✓
```

---

## ✨ KEUNTUNGAN REFACTORING INI

| Aspek | Before | After |
|-------|--------|-------|
| **Modularity** | ❌ Logic campur | ✅ Separated concerns |
| **Testability** | ⚠️ Sulit test | ✅ Easy to mock services |
| **Maintainability** | ❌ Hard to find code | ✅ Clear organization |
| **Scalability** | ⚠️ Main.py jadi besar | ✅ Easy to add features |
| **Reusability** | ❌ Hard to reuse | ✅ Services can be called from anywhere |
| **IDE Navigation** | ❌ Slow | ✅ Fast with clear structure |

